Template: tt-local-generator/hf-token
Type: password
Default:
Description: HuggingFace access token (optional for Qwen3-0.6B)
 The Qwen3-0.6B model (~1.2 GB) is fully public — no token or account
 is required to download it.
 .
 If you already have a HuggingFace token available (e.g. from installing
 another tt-model-* package), it will be reused automatically to avoid
 API rate limits. You do not need to enter anything here.
 .
 Your token is used once and immediately discarded — it is not stored.
